resources.string:
The IEEE PES University Student Branch is a student-run group, under the able guidance of Prof. Divya Rao A at PES University under the worldwide IEEE banner. It is affiliated to the IEEE Bangalore Section and falls under Region 10(Asia Pacific) of the IEEE.

We regularly conduct workshops, technical activities and industrial visits that bring together students of similar interests and create an atmosphere of cohesive learning.

We are driven by the common enthusiasm to stay toe to toe with the latest in the field of technology and through this to stay true to the motto of IEEE – ‘Advancing Technology for Humanity’
